 succeeded in 0ms:
   620	
   621	- **Gitea integration** as the workers' actual git remote (deferred
   622	  to a follow-up sub-chunk after 10d).
   623	- **Experiment-specific images** for the LLM implementer's sandbox
   624	  (10d).
   625	- **Control-plane registration** (Phase 12).
   626	- **Postgres connection pooling** (single connection per store
   627	  instance is fine for one orchestrator + one task-store-server).
   628	- **Multi-replica orchestrator coordination** (Phase 12).
   629	- **Resource limits** on Compose services (10d when LLM workers
